<div class="enlarge_measure">
    <div class="img_wrap">
        <img data-original="https://media.npr.org/assets/img/2015/11/02/berniemayor-1443721908-78_wide-fcf6eaffa21ee6b5ee20a77958be09ba1026c06d-s1200.jpg" alt="Burlington in 1981 was a stratified city, geographically and economically." />
    </div>
